						<summary>

						<p>This inscription refers to the gift of land as <hi rend="italic">kāṇiyāṭchi</hi> to <hi rend="italic">Taṭṭāṉ</hi> Kaṉṉimalai Āchāri, the gold smith-cum-blacksmith of Āttūr for maintaining services rendered in the temple at Tirukkōlakkuḍi.</p>						

